003cspan\u003eNext, chicken stock, lemon juice and cream. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThrow in some uncooked gnocchi and stir stir stir. The sauce thickens and the pasta cooks!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAdd in tons of fresh lemon zest for that zingy bright flavor. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-11-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"creamy lemon gnocchi\" width=\"1741\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/one-pot-creamy-lemon-gnocchi/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"One Pot Creamy Lemon Gnocchi.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-11-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-11-scaled.jpg 1741w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-11-728x920.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-11-768x971.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-11-1215x1536.jpg 1215w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-11-1620x2048.jpg 1620w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-11-150x190.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1741px) 100vw, 1741px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201741%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-11-scaled.jpg 1741w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-11-728x920.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-11-768x971.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-11-1215x1536.jpg 1215w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-11-1620x2048.jpg 1620w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-11-150x190.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-11-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFinally, stir in all the parmesan until it melts. Oh my word. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eServe it up with some fresh basil, more parm, crushed red pepper… yum yum yum. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis is so delicious and super easy. It’s a lovely little side dish but I would also gladly eat it for dinner. An embarrassingly easy solo dinner – it’s perfect for that. Maybe add some toasted sourdough! \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-98041\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-9-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"creamy lemon gnocchi\" width=\"1638\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/one-pot-creamy-lemon-gnocchi/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"One Pot Creamy Lemon Gnocchi.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-9-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-9-scaled.jpg 1638w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-9-728x978.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-9-768x1031.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-9-1144x1536.jpg 1144w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-9-1525x2048.jpg 1525w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-9-150x201.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1638px) 100vw, 1638px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201638%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-9-scaled.jpg 1638w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-9-728x978.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-9-768x1031.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-9-1144x1536.jpg 1144w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-9-1525x2048.jpg 1525w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-9-150x201.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-9-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnd that’s dinner! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-10-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"creamy lemon gnocchi\" width=\"1814\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/one-pot-creamy-lemon-gnocchi/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"One Pot Creamy Lemon Gnocchi.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-10-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-10-scaled.jpg 1814w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-10-728x883.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-10-768x932.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/creamy-lemon-gnocchi-10-1266x1536.jpg 1266